OL,3,CThree-week delay in finding soldier's
OL,4,Cbody in barracks 'unforgivable'
OL,6,FConcluding the inquest, coroner Jon
OL,7,FHeath said he was unable to say with
OL,8,Fsufficient certainty that L/Cpl Mongan
OL,9,Fhad taken his own life and recorded an
OL,10,Fopen conclusion.
OL,12,FSpeaking afterwards, L/Cpl Mongan's
OL,13,Fwife Beth criticised the army's
OL,14,Ffailings.
OL,16,F"I know they've apologised, but it
OL,17,Fdoesn't take away the fact that
OL,18,Fthey've failed him in that front and
OL,19,Fforever will be unforgivable," she
OL,20,Fsaid.
