OL,3,CThree-week delay in finding soldier's
OL,4,Cbody in barracks 'unforgivable'
OL,6,FThe inquest heard evidence from former
OL,7,Fcorporal Stephen Timmerman, who lived
OL,8,Fin the same accommodation block as L/
OL,9,FCpl Mongan, that he was "downgraded"
OL,10,Fby superior officers, and that
OL,11,F"bullying would be an understatement".
OL,13,FAfter an Army investigation into L/Cpl
OL,14,FMongan's death in 2021, Mrs Mongan
OL,15,Fsaid her husband "felt bullied" and
OL,16,Fwas "telling people he was afraid".
OL,18,FThe inquest heard L/Cpl Mongan had
OL,19,Fattempted to kill himself several
OL,20,Fyears earlier when his marriage was
OL,21,Fbreaking down.
