OL,6,FIn the days before he was last seen in
OL,7,FJanuary 2020 he gave away his Nintendo
OL,8,Fto a friend's son, told another friend
OL,9,Fhe "had bought pills but not taken
OL,10,Fthem," and made two donations to a
OL,11,Fsuicide charity.
OL,13,FThe two most likely causes of death
OL,14,Fwere self-inflicted poisoning, after
OL,15,Fbarbiturates were found in L/Cpl's
OL,16,Fsystem ` one of which was bought
OL,17,Fillegally ` or a sudden abnormality of
OL,18,Fthe heart.
