OL,4,Cbody in barracks 'unforgivable'
OL,6,FEmma Norton, director of the Centre
OL,7,Ffor Military Justice, represented Mrs
OL,8,FMongan outside court.
OL,10,FShe said it was "shocking and
OL,11,Fappalling" that L/Cpl Mongan lay dead
OL,12,Ffor so long.
OL,14,F"That failure has had terrible
OL,15,Fconsequences today because it has
OL,16,Fmeant that the coroner cannot be
OL,17,Fsatisfied as to the medical cause of
OL,18,FBernie's death," she said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/11
