OL,6,F"We deeply regret and apologise"
OL,8,FThe Army said it was taking action to
OL,9,Fprevent similar cases.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said: "We deeply regret
OL,12,Fand apologise for the shortfalls in
OL,13,Four duty of care towards him, which
OL,14,Fwere clearly unacceptable. We're
OL,15,Fgrateful to HM Coroner for the
OL,16,Fthorough and diligent examination of
OL,17,Fthe circumstances surrounding his
OL,18,Fdeath.
